*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Line left
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Text "           "
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Choice SAUD SAUD $SAUD=off "audioplay "
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Choice SAUP SAUP $SAUP=off "auplay    "
