*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Choice SRPD SRPD $SRPD=off "rplayD    "
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Line center
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Text ""
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Line left
