*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Selection Opt5 multiple
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Choice KFM KFM $KFM=off "kfm icons workaround"
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Line center
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Text "      System Menu"
