*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Text "      System Menu"
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Selection Opt9 single
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Choice GSDIS GSDIS $GSDIS=on "Disabled  "
*FvwmForm-ThemeSettings: Choice GSGTK GSGTK $GSGTK=off "Gtk Menu  "
